                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7849" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0527</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2160 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织设计：为庞氏集团“缘木腾飞”保驾护航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organization design: Escort the &quot; take-offing with wood&quot; of PANG’S GROUP</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈益民，许惠，殷婧钰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏庞氏木业集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织设计；组织结构；林板一体化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Organizational design; Organizational structure; Forest-board integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沭阳县木材加工业在政府的大力扶持下，正在加速向集聚化、高端化、品牌化方向发展，在规模以上的700家左右企业中，庞氏集团的销售额和税收连续荣登榜首。本案例介绍了庞氏集团从最初的金森源木业，经过20年高速发展，不断做强做大，成功布局金森源建筑模板、笨笨猫生态家居、生态农业三大产品系列，致力于打造“林板一体化”的过程；重点描述了庞氏集团“缘木腾飞”后，面临的组织设计困境。本案例旨在通过庞氏集团组织设计的动因、计划安排、推进落实、三种组织图等实践过程的描述，以期为木材加工类企业，提供组织设计解决方案，助力其设计合适的组织结构，为未来赢得竞争优势，获得可持续发展保驾护航。同时，学生通过案例学习，能够更好地掌握组织设计的依据、作用、原则、要素、内容、形式等知识点及其在实际中的灵活运用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the strong support of the government, the wood processing industry of Shuyang County is accelerating to the direction of agglomeration, high end and brand development. PANG’S GROUP ranked first in sales and tax revenue among 700 companies.This case introduces the PANG’S GROUP from the original Jinsenyuan Wood Industry, after 20 years of rapid development, has continued to grow stronger and bigger, and successfully deployed the three major product series of Jinsenyuan Building Formwork, Stupid Cat ecological home, and ecological agriculture, and is committed to creating The process of &quot;integration of forest and board&quot;; it focuses on describing the organizational design dilemma faced by PANG’S GROUP after the&quot; take-offing with wood&quot;.This case aims to provide organizational design solutions for wood processing enterprises and help them design appropriate organizational structures through the description of the motivation, planning, implementation, and three organizational charts of the PANG’S GROUP&#39;s organizational design,so as to gain a competitive advantage for the future and secure sustainable development. At the same time, through case study, students can better grasp the basis, function, principle, element, content, form and other knowledge points of organizational design and their flexible application in practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织设计的概念、作用、依据；组织设计的原则、要求、内容和步骤；PDCA循环；组织设计的形式、特点、适用条件以及组织设计与职位分析的关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
